N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 160.33 - Verification of education

State Regulations

An application for licensure must be verified by a
representative of the approved appearance enhancement school. A school shall
authorize such individual to make such verification, and file such
authorization with the department. Notes
